{"tid":1476812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認唔認同「政府承諾不起訴示威者」，比「成立獨立調查委員會」更重要？","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:52:55.000Z","uid":36494,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b106a5c87d3ef1a4877408425bd51a05e9c910","tid":1476812,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"就算真係有獨立調查委員會<br />\n隨時調查完起訴大量示威者<br />\n就算有幾個高官下台或警犬俾起訴<br />\n對我地來說，都係得不償失<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為一定要政府先承諾不起訴示威者<br />\n否則成立調查委員會對我哋無著數<br />\n<br />\n要先「承諾不起訴示威者」，再「成立獨立調查委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同 ，正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不認同，負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab10c82fe38611e1d76edc0c3b272fe91e83abe","tid":1476812,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"咁姐係只要打住公義嘅旗號就連法律都可以唔理？"},{"pid":"e785aa1f4a02afab83d55ef2c62cdb6b6d6d402c","tid":1476812,"uid":60092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"無真普選無超度自治, 做乜都係晒氣。"},{"pid":"edef483a5ca452a0e4c3185ab2d95cc0343e23e4","tid":1476812,"uid":2854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"5大訴求無分先後"}]}